## Tech Stack (nextjs)

- Next.js 15 (App Router) + TypeScript strict
- Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui
- Vitest + React Testing Library for tests
- Playwright for E2E (optional)
- pnpm for package management

## Architecture

```
src/
  app/           # Next.js App Router pages and layouts
  server/        # tRPC routers, database queries, business logic
  components/    # React components (shadcn/ui based)
  lib/           # Shared utilities, schema, auth config
  __tests__/     # Test files
```

## Additional Conventions

### Testing
- Single Vitest runner for all tests
- Globals enabled (no need to import describe/it/expect)
- `pnpm vitest run <file>` for single file
- Tests in `__tests__/` subdirectories or co-located as `*.test.ts(x)`
